data.text:
Genuine Antique Map

1900

Maker: Rand McNally

Antique printed color map from the Rand McNally Condensed Atlas , published in 1900. Shows cities, large towns, lakes, railroads. With interesting old boundaries (Athabasca, Assiniboia, Keewatin, etc). Very good antique condition with some toning at the paper edges. This small map measures approx. 5.75 x 7 inches to the paper edges.

Item Number: CAN361
